+-------------------+         Push Code         +-------------------+
|  Developer Local   |  ---------------------->  |    GitHub Repo    |
|   (VS Code, etc.) |                            |  (feature branch) |
+-------------------+                            +-------------------+
                                                          |
                                                          |  Trigger GitHub Actions Workflow
                                                          v
                                          +-------------------------------+
                                          | GitHub Actions CI/CD Pipeline  |
                                          |                               |
                                          |  1. Run Bias Check Script      |
                                          |  2. Run PII Check Script       |
                                          |                               |
                                          |   If ALL checks pass:          |
                                          |       ✅ Allow Merge           |
                                          |                               |
                                          |   If ANY check fails:          |
                                          |       ❌ Block Merge           |
                                          |       ✉️ Send Email Alert      |
                                          +-------------------------------+
                                                          |
                                                          v
                                         +-------------------------------+
                                         |    Production / Main Branch    |
                                         +-------------------------------+
